This article is about the upcoming 2022 TV series. For the 1981 TV series, see The Hitchhiker's Guide to the Galaxy (TV series)
The Hitchhiker's Guide to the Galaxy is an upcoming TV series adaptation of the radio show and media of the same name. It is being written and developed by Carlton Cuse and Jason Fuchs for the Hulu streaming platform.https://deadline.com/2019/07/the-hitchhikers-guide-to-the-galaxy-tv-series-in-works-at-hulu-from-carlton-cuse-jason-fuchs-1202652440/ Hulu renewed the series for a second season.https://thedisinsider.com/2020/08/03/hulu-gives-their-hitchhikers-guide-to-the-galaxy-an-early-season-two-renewal/

Production on the first season is set to start in FOX Studios in Los Angeles, with locational shooting being done at Elstree Studios, in the UK.  References 

